      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple. i don't think it's just about \"rebuilding skills\" or \"practicing.\" it feels much deeper than that. when the music stopped/the color died, it felt like the thing that actually made me *me* just evaporated. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just an empty space where a human used to be. if the essence is gone, what's even the point of the rest of it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
